    An effect on a Card.

    • Method Detail

      • getType

        EffectType getType()
        The type of the effect.

        This function will also be used when printing the effect on a GCard.

        Returns:
        The type of the effect.

      • getEffectValue

        int getEffectValue()
        Get the value of the effect.

        This function will also be used when printing the effect on a GCard.

        Returns:
        The value of the effect or 0 if the effect has something to do with blocking.

      • getSelector

        Set<Either<Card,​CardColor>> getSelector()
        Get the cards that are related to this effect.

        A CardColor is a placeholder for all the cards in that cardcolor, except for the card that contains this effect.

        This function will also be used when printing the effect on a GCard.

        Returns:
        The Set of cards and cardcolors related to this effect.
